 />\n同香港啲中小企老世一狗樣擺明就唔想俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以點解港資愈做愈縮,最後等被淘汰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46237d193b1388def262180fb7d281ab8d0f6324","tid":427971,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:53:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99abc153ac77766b75dfd34cfa0f719b40d6e849","tid":427971,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T13:22:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f9d8ac18990076ae85b8845f20390d7a539608","tid":427971,"uid":121580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T13:28:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ON9, 已經係最富都唔撚比多少少,仲要係最低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要幾個月無工開<br />\n都仲想俾最低工資<br />\n俾3倍人工好基本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n產量3倍你唔係俾唔起3倍人工下化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e8e27ccfa8f875108dfb9cd19ba9524973c124","tid":427971,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T14:08:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Oct8近期活躍五毛<br />\nJR<br />\n三色貓<br />\n民國復興<br />\n拜仁慕尼黑<br />\n蘇麗珊<br />\n國語好手<br />\nbb chu<br />\nRedbaron<br />\nnewlife<br />\n優美開始<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"dccc25331f61bf8b185d022ffee553ed6508787c","tid":427971,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T00:05:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ON9, 已經係最富都唔撚比多少少,仲要係最低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要幾個月無工開<br />\n都仲想俾最低工資<br />\n俾3倍人工好基本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n產量3倍你唔係俾唔起3倍人工下化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br